name: AVAudioUnitEQFilterType
desc: Filter types available to use with the filter type property.

items.name: case parametric
items.desc: A type that represents a parametric filter that derives from a Butterworth analog prototype.

items.name: case lowPass
items.desc: A type that represents a simple Butterworth second-order low-pass filter.

items.name: case highPass
items.desc: A type that represents a simple Butterworth second-order high-pass filter.

items.name: case resonantLowPass
items.desc: A type that represents a low-pass filter with resonance support using the bandwidth parameter.

items.name: case resonantHighPass
items.desc: A type that represents a high-pass filter with resonance support using the bandwidth parameter.

items.name: case bandPass
items.desc: A type that represents a bandpass filter.

items.name: case bandStop
items.desc: A type that represents a band-stop filter, also known as a notch filter.

items.name: case lowShelf
items.desc: A type that represents a low-shelf filter.

items.name: case highShelf
items.desc: A type that represents a high-shelf filter.

items.name: case resonantLowShelf
items.desc: A type that represents a low-shelf filter with resonance support using the bandwidth parameter.

items.name: case resonantHighShelf
items.desc: A type that represents a high-shelf filter with resonance support using the bandwidth parameter.
